    <p>
      On this one I am trying to have three divs in a flexbox with them being
      adjusted with space-between but the center one staying in center no matter
      what ! if you want to know how I did it, definetley check the source ! :)
    </p>
    <div class="flex-container1">
      <div class="a1">1</div>
      <div class="a1 center1">2</div>
      <div class="a1">Lorem ipsum dolor</div>
    </div>
    <h1>Experiment 2 :</h1>
    <p>
      Here I am trying to apply an effect when either of the items in the div
      are hovered !
    </p>
    <div class="container2">
      <div class="item12">logo</div>
      <div class="item22">site title</div>
    </div>
    <h1>Experiment 3 :</h1>
    <p>
      here I am trying to see if grandsons of a tag are count as childs of the
      tag in css !
    </p>
    <div class="container3">
      father
      <div class="son3">
        son
        <div class="grandson3">grandson</div>
      </div>
